channel.title: [317] help on adding GE [317]
channel.description:
:confused:
ok so i have been trying to add the grandexchange onto my 317 server for months now. i've tried so many things and have looked on almost all runescape private server help pages to find a good guide. i have been trying to add a grandexchange, like in gangstascape and butters dream.
(if you need a visual aid on what i want/need here you go)
GangstaScape- http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,311002.0.html
Butters Dream- http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,304799.0.html
i JUST really want a GrandExchange like they added..if anyone knows of a tutorial on the fourms, or a tutorial that they now, please PM me or leave a reply for me..thanks and the reason i don't like those servers, and people are problay going to say "why don't u use those sources?" because i worked hard on mine and i just want the grandexchange lol...so any1 who knows a guide PLEASE POST!!!!!!
thanks! ...please..
